1.summary: Software Engineering Intern position at Google for Summer 2025
1.title: Internship Offer from Google
1.action: Accept offer through candidate portal, complete background check, submit required documents
1.original_body:
---------- Forwarded message ---------
From: Aswin Vishwaa <aswinvishwaa@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, Oct 4, 2025, 2:23 PM
Subject: Subject: Congratulations! Internship Offer from Google
To: <aswinvishwaa415@gmail.com>


Dear Candidate,
                      We are pleased to offer you a Software Engineering
Internship position at Google for Summer 2025.
Position: Software Engineering Intern
Duration: June 1, 2025 - August 31, 2025
Stipend: $8,000/month
Location: Mountain View, CA

 Please review the attached offer letter and accept the offer by April 15,
2025 through our candidate portal.
 Action Required:
1. Accept offer by April 15, 2025
2. Complete background check
3. Submit required documents

 We're excited to have you join our team!
 Best regards,
Google Recruiting Team
